name: GRN Inwards Report
query:
Select grn.name,grn.grn_date,grn.grn_time,grn.supplier,grn.supplier_name,grn.purchase_receipt,det.part_number,det.item_name,det.lot_no as MainLot,det.batch_no as ChildLot,det.qty,grn.purchase_order,grn.supplier_invoice_no,grn.supplier_invoice_date 
from `tabGRN Inward` grn join `tabGRN Inward Item Details` det ON(grn.name=det.parent and grn.docstatus=1)
